    "created_at": "2025-09-29T16:36:46Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-09-29T16:36:59Z",
    "body": "> It is not module-level, but it is [already possible to use `prev_fg` and `prev_bg`](https://starship.rs/advanced-config/#style-strings).\n\nThanks so much for pointing this out! Somehow I didn't fine this in the docs.\n\nAnd for the record it does support inheriting colors from other modules, as long as they're placed next to each other:\n\n```toml\n[nodejs]\nsymbol = \" \"\nformat = \"([](bg:#339933 fg:prev_bg)[ $symbol$version ](bg:prev_bg fg:color_fg0))\"\n```",
    "author_association": "NONE",
